title: Finally, F1 is back! Austrian GP and 2020 season preview
description: After eight months, F1 will go racing again at the Austrian GP this weekend. ESPN's Alexis Nunes, Nate Saunders and Laurence Edmondson give their predictions and everything you need to know about F1’s ‘new normal'. The team will also react to some of your Pit Stop predictions and questions.
